OL,3,CNorth Sea sandstone could be used to
OL,4,Cstore carbon dioxide, report says
OL,6,FIt works by capturing carbon dioxide
OL,7,Fat the source, transporting it and
OL,8,Fthen injecting it into suitable rock
OL,9,Fformations deep beneath the surface,
OL,10,Ftypically at depths of more than 800
OL,11,Fmetres.
OL,13,FBGS geologists are working to better
OL,14,Funderstand the subsurface geology of
OL,15,Fthe central North Sea and its
OL,16,Fsuitability for storing carbon dioxide
OL,17,Fcaptured from major industrial sources.
