OL,3,CNorth Sea sandstone could be used to
OL,4,Cstore carbon dioxide, report says
OL,6,FThe work could release one of the UK's
OL,7,Flargest carbon storage resources which
OL,8,Fthe BGS said could underpin the
OL,9,FGovernment's #21.7 billion investment
OL,10,Fin CCS projects.
OL,12,FJohn Williams, senior geoscientist at
OL,13,FBGS, said: "With relatively few
OL,14,Flicences currently issued in the
OL,15,Fcentral North Sea, robust pre-
OL,16,Fcompetitive geological understanding
OL,17,Fis essential to realise the region's
OL,18,Fstorage potential.
