OL,6,FThe BGS would also have to look at the
OL,7,Feffectiveness of the vital sealing
OL,8,Flayers above and between the sandstone
OL,9,Fformations, which might be prone to
OL,10,Fdisruption by various geological
OL,11,Fphenomena and legacy oil and gas
OL,12,Fwells, which could act as pathways for
OL,13,FCO2 to escape if not properly assessed.
